videos.description: De'Aaron Fox takes the ball up the court and makes the nice layup off the glass over two Florida defenders.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Fox sinks layup in traffic

videos.description: Florida head coach Mike White discusses adjustments his team needs to make in the 2nd half against Kentucky.
videos.headline: Mike White on his team's offensive performance in the 1st half

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox goes out running and gets the layup to go plus the foul.
videos.headline: Fox uses his speed in transition for the layup

videos.description: Florida's Canyon Barry knocks down a 3-Pointer assisted by Chris Chiozza.
videos.headline: Florida extends their lead on a Canyon Barry 3-Pointer

videos.description: Florida comes up with the steal and Chris Chiozza sees Kasey Hill all alone who dunks it in.
videos.headline: Defensive pressure leads to fastbreak dunk by Florida's Hill

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza finds Devin Robinson in transition for a 2-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Chiozza's behind-the-back pass sets up a Robinson slam

videos.description: John Calipari's Wildcats are handed a 22-point upset from the No. 24 Gators thanks to Kasey Hill's 21-point night.
videos.headline: No. 24 Florida upsets No. 8 Kentucky by 22
